    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps at MRL 5, the assessment team accepted the package for submission based on the Monte Carlo UQ results demonstrating hemolysis index remains below the clinical threshold across the uncertainty envelope at the 95th percentile. Remaining gaps are documented as open actions for the next assessment cycle. The hemolysis model validation approach referenced in the literature (including methods described in related prior work) supports the overall modeling framework even where direct validation data are unavailable.",
